  "keyFeatures": [
    "Modular hook system targeting ps_game.exe, ps_dbAgent.exe, ps_login.exe, and Game.exe",
    "EP6.4 equipment slots, shape packets, and protocol compatibility",
    "Raid 150 — expands party size from 30 to 150 users with matching client UI",
    "Declarative INI-based configuration for enchant cap, level cap, battlefields, roulette, and item synthesis",
    "Cross-faction whisper, trade, inspect, and login support",
    "ImGui roulette panel, Discord RPC, and emoji/GIF chat integration",
    "Custom item effects: recreation runes, safety charms, ability transfer, chaotic square synthesis",
    "Item set synergy system with server-side SetItem.SData loading",
    "Extended client commands: /font, /wings, /pets, /costumes, /effects, /fpsboost, /titles, /colour",
    "Memory patching utilities (detour, read_memory, write_memory) used across all modules"
  ],
